strategies: I simply tried to recall as many associations as possible. I noticed right away that some icons were used more frequently than others (leaves; crayfish; palm trees; train).

comments: Nothing was too difficult or boring. I felt engaged the entire way through. The images helped with that! They were fun and lifelike.
